      <h1 class='title'>Tenancy Deposits</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 28 November 2002 vol 395 c54WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_54ws' title='Col. 54WS &mdash; HC Deb 28 November 2002 vol 395 c54WS' name='column_54ws' href='#column_54ws' rel='bookmark'>54WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0395P2_20021128_CWS_16'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tony-mcnulty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0395P2_20021128_CWS_16' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tony McNulty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tony-mcnulty" title="Mr Tony McNulty">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State, Office of the Deputy Prime Minister (Mr. Tony McNulty)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I am pleased to announce today the publication of a consultation paper on tenancy deposits. The research report on the pilot tenancy deposit scheme is also to be published in the week beginning 16 December. Summaries of both documents are also being published today. Copies of these documents will be placed in the Library of the House. The consultation paper will initiate a debate on what action might be taken to address disputes over tenancy deposits.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
